subject: Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race (Alaska)
Dog Sledding
lead_paragraph: Dallas Seavey won the Iditarod for the third time in four years, crossing the finish line in Nome, Alaska, in 8 days 8 hours 13 minutes 6 seconds.
